title: American horror story coven -  queenie betrays Delphine 7x3
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: The fact that a show made us feel bad for a monstrous person really shows how good Bates and the writers are
while she absolutely did deserve this for everything she's done, i still can't help but feel bad just because it seemed like she was genuinely changing and trying to be a better person.
Holy crap. Does Angela Bassett age at all? She is DROP DEAD GORGEOUS!!!
Delphine literally deserved this but somehow Kathy Bates had so much character development that we forgot that. Truly impressive.
I hate how this happened to Delphine, especially because she was showing character development from her disgusting ways and was growing to become great friends with Queenie.
